<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>لا تَختَشِ مِن ضَياعٍ ... فالله يَحفَظُ عَبدَه<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
